uring this season, and the resulting resort portfolio sold for $1.5 billion.</p>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3019\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES-st7new.jpg\" alt=\"Seize the Seven Landing Page\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3017\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_FEATURED.jpg\" alt=\"WPR Website\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2817\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_St72.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>WINTER 17/18 WEB LANDING PAGE DESIGN</h2>\r\n<strong>Goals:</strong> Winter Park was seeking a landing page where guests could easily see all there is to do in Winter Park and plan their vacation. This page supports Winter Park as a destination while driving both resort and local ancillary businesses.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2835\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_1718LandingPage.jpg\" alt=\"WPR Landing Page\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2836\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_1718LandingPage2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>BILLBOARD:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3016\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_Billboard.jpg\" alt=\"Winter Park Billboard\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>_________</h2>\r\n<h2>SEASON PASS MAILER:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2837\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_Mailer1.jpg\" alt=\"Winter Park Resort Pass Mailer\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2838\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_Mailer2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>CUSTOM FIT SKI RENTALS - VAN WRAP:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2851\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_Van.jpg\" alt=\"Winter Park Van\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>WINTER PARK GROUPS - VENUE FLIER:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2853\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_Groups1.jpg\" alt=\"Winter Park Resort Groups Flier\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2854\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_Groups2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>\'17 SPRINGTOPIA T-SHIRT:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2965\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/SPRINTOPIA-SHIRT-1.jpg\" alt=\"Springtopia Shirt\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>\'18 UPHILL BATTLE T-SHIRT:</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3173\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_UphillBattle.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>SEVEN TERRITORY BUFF:</h2>\r\nCreated with elements from the badges of the Seven Territories of Winter Park Resort.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2966\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/WPR-WEBSITE-IMAGES_Buff.jpg\" alt=\"Winter Park Buff\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>SEVEN TERRITORY POWDER SKIS:</h2>\r\nCreated using photos from all Seven Territories at Winter Park Resort. The Terr