/charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ETG-WEBSITE-IMAGES_POSTER.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2825\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ETG-WEBSITE-IMAGES_WEBSITE.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2826\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ETG-WEBSITE-IMAGES_WEBSITE2.jpg\" alt=\"Eat the guts\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2827\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ETG-WEBSITE-IMAGES_ETG-STICKERS.jpg\" alt=\"Eat the guts stickers\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" />\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>TRAILER &amp; FULL FILM:</h2>\r\n<h6>Edited by: Charles Stemen</h6>\r\n<h6>Filmed By: Liam McKinley &amp; John Hayes</h6>\r\n[embed]https://vimeo.com/232407005[/embed]\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n[embed]https://vimeo.com/245654902[/embed]\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>FILM NOMINATIONS:</h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://festivalif3.com/the-nominees-for-the-10th-edition-of-the-if3-movie-awards-are/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">International Freeski Film Festival</a>:\r\n\r\n<strong>DISCOVERY OF THE YEAR</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>BEST SHORT MOVIE</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>STANDOUT URBAN MOVIE</strong>\r\n<h2>__________</h2>\r\n<h2>FILM REVIEWS:</h2>\r\n<em>\"The film is raw without artifice, without romance and with the freedom that offers a production without sponsors.\"</em>\r\n\r\n- <a href=\"https://www.highfive-festival.com/en/cinema-en/eat-the-guls/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">High Five Film Festival</a>\r\n\r\n<em>\"...A masterpiece</em><em>\"</em>\r\n\r\n- <span class=\"fwn fcg\"><span class=\"fcg\"><span class=\"fwb\"><a id=\"js_69\" class=\"profileLink\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/magnus.graner.3/posts/10155496989819079\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;l&quot;}\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/user.php?id=559439078&amp;extragetparams=%7B%22hc_ref%22%3A%22ARRCrYXIxrC4fjsH3oQQfbNS4aEnn9gmuLTwBOi3VJznwWL1TL4iXSBYH5V3OCR8KfQ%22%7D\" data-hovercard-prefer-more-content-show=\"1\" data-hovercard-referer=\"ARRCrYXIxrC4fjsH3oQQfbNS4aEnn9gmuLTwBOi3VJznwWL1TL4iXSBYH5V3OCR8KfQ\" aria-controls=\"js_67\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-describedby=\"js_68\">Magnus Granér</a></span> </span></span>\r\n\r\n<em>\"One of the best ski movies ever, not just this year</em><em>\"</em>\r\n\r\n- <a href=\"https://www.newschoolers.com/member/Jhaek.254289/Profile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"tag mc_0 md_0\">Jhaek</span></a>\r\n\r\n<em>\"First cult classic ski movie in years, this is one of those </em><em>you just watch over and over. I am sure years from now this will still be timeless given the creativity and artistic value it presents. On my 5th watch, like it more each time. There is something new I appreciate in each and every segment each watch.\"</em>\r\n\r\n- <a href=\"https://www.newschoolers.com/member/MaineLandCollab.20034/Profile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"tag mc_0 md_0\">MaineLandCollab</span></a>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Truly a work of art that will last throughout history. A piece that will be used as an example for the younger generations of what to strive for.\"</em>\r\n\r\n- <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/flatstanley_8/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Oscar Seagram</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','EAT THE GUTS','','publish','closed','closed','','eat-the-guts','','','2017-12-21 19:23:00','2017-12-21 19:23:00','',0,'http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/?post_type=portfolio&#038;p=2819',0,'portfolio','',0),(2823,2,'2017-12-07 21:15:43','2017-12-07 21:15:43','','ETG-WEBSITE-IMAGES_LOGO','','inherit','open','closed','','etg-website-images_logo','','','2017-12-07 21:15:52','2017-12-07 21:15:52','',2819,'http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/ETG-WEBSITE-IMAGES_LOGO.jpg',