_0398.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1603\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Our first view of Dead Dog. Holy hell.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3083\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_3164.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2193\" height=\"1910\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>My line in red, Zachs in yellow.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3086\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_3164_Route.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1525\" /></h6>\r\n<h6> Myself on the final steps to the summit. (Photo: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zach Cohen</a>)<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3080\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0402.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach cheesin w/ some bloody teeth :)<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3082\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_1673.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Gopro Screenshot from the peak looking down. Dead Dog is out of sight to the left under the cliff.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3078\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/91630DC1-CA79-48F5-AA5E-0047ADD68329.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>In the couloir:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3077\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/76821DC9-7775-47BA-90C4-D5D3E5844BA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>(Photo: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zach Cohen</a>)<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3081\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0403.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"3024\" height=\"3063\" /></h6>','TORREYS PEAK - DEAD DOG COULOIR','','publish','open','open','','torreys-peak-dead-dog-couloir','','','2017-12-25 15:56:33','2017-12-25 15:56:33','',0,'http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/?p=3004',0,'post','',0),(3005,2,'2017-09-30 17:33:15','2017-09-30 17:33:15','After September graced the front range peaks with some snow, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zach Cohen</a> &amp; I headed up Kelso Ridge for some spicy, snowy, icy &amp; wet 3rd/4th class scrambling. We didn\'t do a great job at photographing the crux sections. We were probably too puckered.\r\n<h6>Grays Peak on the left, Torreys on the Right. Kelso Ridge is the ridgeline straight up from the photo on the right.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3056\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8325.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Looks Badass:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3057\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8327.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"795\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach topping out on one of the more 5thish class sections:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3058\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8334.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2000\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Myself ascending a snowier section of the route: (photo:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Zach Cohen</a>)<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3055\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0912.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1816\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach topping out on another fun scramble with Grays in the background:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3059\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8339.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1129\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Zach approaching the crux:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3060\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8340.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2000\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>View from the summit with Grays Peak in the foreground.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3061\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_8344.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"937\" /></h6>','TORREYS PEAK - KELSO RIDGE','','publish','open','open','','torreys-peak-kelso-ridge','','','2017-12-23 19:27:08','2017-12-23 19:27:08','',0,'http://charlesstemen.wpengine.com/?p=3005',0,'post','',0),(3006,2,'2017-04-08 17:58:24','2017-04-08 17:58:24','<h6>Above: Myself making my way down the Left Sister. (Photo: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zach Cohen</a>)</h6>\r\n<h6>The Approach:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3072\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/IMG_6419.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"782\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3068\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/015AEF9C-DD4A-4944-BF82-A584C8D97525-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2402\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Myself following Zach up the Left Sister (Photo: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/303zachary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Zach Cohen</a>)<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3071\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_E0659.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1524\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3069\" src=\"http://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Edited_IMG_0662.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"3024\" height=\"4032\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>Just the tip. I am skiing on HG Skis \"powder ski\" the EL, available <a href=\"http://hgskis.com/?ski=junkyard-el\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>. It\'s extremely versatile for how wide it is. Shoot me an <a href=\"http://charlesstemen.com/about-us-02/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">email</a> for a discount code.<img class=\"aligncenter size-ful