ass=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3129\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.02.11_RossPeak-BananaCouloir_Cstemen_Iphone_IMG_2701.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1853\" /></h6>\n<h6>_____</h6>\n<h6>A rough overview of our route, the lower line is our approach. We probably traversed under the couloir earlier than I drew it below. On the way back we were lured into the other drainage with hopes of delaying skinning for longer. It didn\'t delay it much though, and we soon found ourselves skinning out of a  <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3134\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Route.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2040\" height=\"1440\" /></h6>','ROSS PEAK - BANANA COULOIR','','inherit','closed','closed','','3128-autosave-v1','','','2018-02-13 15:48:18','2018-02-13 15:48:18','',3128,'http://charlesstemen.com/3128-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3136,2,'2018-02-16 21:48:12','2018-02-16 21:48:12','I was able to spend some of the nicer days of the month shooting photos for <a href=\"https://www.winterparkresort.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Winter Park Resort</a>. Below are a few of my favorites. Thanks to all of the skiers and riders that helped me out. Here\'s to more snow!\r\n<h6>Above: First tracks down Eagle Wind\'s trees.</h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Taking in the views of the beautiful Parry\'s peak after a fresh coating of snow:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3137\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_IMG_0024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>I love the small rolls and pillows in the Eagle Wind Territory, especially when you catch first tracks :)<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3151\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/EWT_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC05348_BlueSky.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2998\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3140\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_IMG_9761.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>The never-ending search for more powder:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3141\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_IMG_9878.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2060\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3143\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.22_CStemenDSC05763.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1975\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Picking our way down the legendary Mary Jane in a fresh coating of snow:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3144\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.22_CStemenDSC05997.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1789\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Blake loves Mary Jane:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3145\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.22_CStemenDSC06034.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3146\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.22_CStemenDSC06076.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2998\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3147\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.22_CStemenDSC06091.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3148\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/18.01.24_CStemenDSC06431.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3149\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/EWT_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC05160.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1547\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3150\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/EWT_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC05284_BlueSky.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1423\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Colorado\'s Top Adventure Town:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3152\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Fence_Panorama.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"914\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Nothing better than a party shred with a good homie:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3153\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC04952.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1589\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Especially when they go down and not you.<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3155\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC05107.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1947\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Untracked cold smoke:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3156\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC05183.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1741\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>That feeling when you find that untouched hallway in the trees. It\'s always a good one:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3157\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC05200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2272\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Welcome to Mary Jane:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3158\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_18.01.11_CStemen_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC05384.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3159\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_18.01.11_CStemen_MJT_18.01.11_CStemen_DSC04709.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2211\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3160\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_Panoramic_CStemen_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1796\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Parry\'s Peek providing some pow slashes on the side of the trail with the gorgeous out-of-bounds Zero Creek lures in the background:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3161\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/PBT_18.01.07_CStemen_PBT_18.01.07_CStemen_DSC04465.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1501\" /><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3165\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/HEADER_WPT_18.01.24_CStemen_DSC06390.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"7952\" height=\"5304\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>We sat here for 10+ minutes waiting for the sun and clouds to clear. It didn\'t quite happen, but nobody came to poach our tracks either. Y\'all need to step up your powder hunting game :):<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3167\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/MJT_Panorama_1_CropExample.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1513\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Zero Creek thoo....<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3162\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/PBT_18.01.07_CStemen_PBT_18.01.07_CStemen_IMG_9637.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" /></h6>\r\n<h6>_____</h6>\r\n<h6>Coming out of Parsenn Bowl can lead you into thick trees, or wide hallways. We found the latter:<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3163\" src=\"https://charlesstemen.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/PBT_18.01.11_CStemen_IMG_9882.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" /></h6>\r\nThanks for taking a peek. To hire me to shoot photos, please email me: charles@charlesstemen.com','JANUARY at WINTER PARK RESORT','','publish','open','open','','january-at-winter-park-resort','','','2018-02-16 23:50:44','2018-02-16 23:50:44','',0,'http://charlesstemen.com/?p=3136',0,'post','',2),(3137,2,'2018-02-16 21:28:40','2018-02-16 